sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant CRON as GitHub Actions cron
  participant CLI as post-daily-top10 CLI
  participant TKN as TikTok (open.tiktokapis.com)<br/>POST /v2/oauth/token/
  participant CP as TikTok Content Posting API<br/>open.tiktokapis.com

  CRON->>CLI: 30 21 * * * UTC
  CLI->>CLI: load TIKTOK_REFRESH_TOKEN from env
  CLI->>TKN: POST /v2/oauth/token/<br/>grant_type=refresh_token
  TKN-->>CLI: new access_token + rotated refresh_token
  CLI->>CLI: persist rotated refresh_token (gh secret set OR .env.local rewrite)<br/>BEFORE any further network call
  CLI->>CP: POST inbox/video/init OR post/publish/video/init<br/>Authorization: Bearer access_token
  CP-->>CLI: { publish_id, upload_url }
  CLI->>CP: PUT upload_url with MP4 bytes
  CLI->>CP: POST publish/status/fetch (poll until terminal)
  CP-->>CLI: SEND_TO_USER_INBOX or PUBLISH_COMPLETE
